Tributes for Coach Smith poured in from all over the sporting world in a series of messages on social media.

Tar Heels senior Jackson Simmons wrote on Instagram that Smith's 'impact on the game is one that will stand the test of time.'

Fellow UNC alum Harrison Barnes also honored the late coach by tweeting  thanks for all the things you stood for and believed in #CarolinaWay.'  

Born on February 28, 1931, in Emporia, Kansas, Dean Edwards Smith was the son of public school teachers. 

